OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBrightest first thing, with the
OL,6,Fbest of limited sunny spells in the
OL,7,Fnortheast. Cloud generally increasing
OL,8,Ffrom the west through the day, with
OL,9,Fthe wind picking up, although it
OL,10,Fshould stay dry. Feeling warm after a
OL,11,Fchilly start in places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBecoming windy during the
OL,14,Fevening, with blustery sharp showers
OL,15,Fmaking inroads eastwards. Clearer
OL,16,Fspells developing in the west towards
OL,17,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
